Decodium/Raptor reference material
=================================

MadModem v1.10 includes selected reference material and small C++/Qt ports
inspired by the Decodium 3.0 "Shannon" source package supplied by the user.
The relevant Decodium components are:

- Network/NtpClient.cpp and Network/NtpClient.hpp: asynchronous UDP NTP client
  with multiple servers, RTT filtering, median/IQR offset selection and HTTP
  Date fallback.
- Palettes/Raptor.pal and qmlitems/WaterfallItem.cpp: Raptor-style waterfall
  colour mapping.

Decodium is GPL-licensed; COPYING is included in this directory. MadModem is
already distributed as a GPLv3 combined package because of the MSHV-derived FT8
code. The files under port/ are adapted for MadModem's Qt Widgets application;
the unmodified originals used as reference are kept under reference/.

v1.12 additions
---------------
For the focused FT4/FT8 work, selected Decodium 3.0 Shannon FT4 reference
source files are retained under:

  third_party/decodium_gpl/reference/lib/ft4/
  third_party/decodium_gpl/reference/lib/ft4_decode.f90

FT2 reference material from the previous experimental timing-shell step is not
part of the active v1.12 package.  MadModem v1.12 focuses on FT4 and FT8.
